name: ORD_FRQ_OVRD_REL
description: For frequency overrides that have a different set of times on each day, this table gives the times for each day.

columns.name: ORDER_ID
columns.description: The unique ID of the procedure order record that was reviewed.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: EFQ_OVRD_REL_DAYS
columns.description: Contains the days for a frequency override. Column EFQ_OVRD_REL_TIMES specifies the times for these days.

columns.name: EFQ_OVRD_REL_TIME
columns.description: Contains the times for a frequency override. Column EFQ_OVRD_REL_DAYS specifies the days for these times.
